{"type": "article", "id": 13892, "title": "视频辅助设备", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-24T08:03:09Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 45, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606154018lWkEIq93opJN4GHh.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tFrankly 是一家来自瑞典的公司，这是他们最近推出的一款视频辅助设备，它被安装在手机摄像头上，可以把视频的画面扩大 50％，同时，在光照不足的条件下可以自动调整照明环境，自动补光，并且不会对画面质量造成伤害，从而为视频带来更为舒适的体验。它适用于所有的电脑和智能移动端，通过蓝牙和设备进行连接，使用 USB 充电。<a href=\"http://www.getaviw.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看详细信息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141532BRCGnVsNPtfJU2rZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55867971\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261415322vqBbcFi894JazT1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56234719\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141533qL8GvrdjK4YS10Ui.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56234719\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141534Pfu3ybM8gEYwcqN7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141534DfV0GRNElTeHxK7g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56234719\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141535gsyFhbdtDIUVKNnf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141536q4L2znRrSyACdX8g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75427873\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}